cdata.name: Farad
cdata.desc:
Farad is an ultra-capacitors (high power density energy storage device) manufacturer.

FRD is an Ethereum-based ERC20 token backed by the production of the supra-mentioned ultra-capacitors in Farad'sChina-basedfactory. Farad linked theirdigital tokens to real-life economic production.The FRD represents the right to the contract 'manufacturing and sales agency agreement' to produce Ultra-Capacitor Cells (UCC) with an output of 1,600,000,000 mF over a period of 36 months. Each FRDis equivalent to 1mili-Faraday (mF) that each cell for ultra-capacitor will generate.
